name: Phil's Gas Station
description:
The advent of flying cars spawned many gas stations like Phil's. Hastily build on top of the
tallest buildings with an abundance of glowing signage, they overlooked cloudscapes for
decades. Many saw them as eyesores, but there was a certain charm to their retro
aesthetics. Once electric cars took over these stations became deserted, now they remain
lonely beacons of the past, cruising through the stratosphere.
